# Catacombs Skip

Catacombs skips allow you to skip the major part of the catacombs.

## External Resources

#### Glitchless Versions

- Glitchless version ( very difficult ): [https://youtu.be/BVtYZBgG0Wo](https://youtu.be/BVtYZBgG0Wo) by m3dic on YouTube
- Glitchless version (easy): [https://youtu.be/38Oipc17ErY](https://youtu.be/38Oipc17ErY) by m3dic on YouTube

#### Glitched Versions

This version abuse the [fall damage cancels](/ds1remaster/fall-damages-cancel).

- Glitched version (delayed roll setup):  [https://youtu.be/X2NwsNKbLY0](https://youtu.be/X2NwsNKbLY0) by aeiou on YouTube
- Glitched version (memeroll setup): [https://youtu.be/LhZO6uND8wI](https://youtu.be/LhZO6uND8wI) by minitius on YouTube
